Interface GeoCodeService


  • public interface GeoCodeService
    Interface utilized by Retrofit to make requests to the web-services consumed by the Food Fail Application.

      Requests full address and geological coordinates from the Google Geocding API.

    • Method Detail

      • getLatLng

        @GET(value="/maps/api/geocode/json")
retrofit2.Call<Result> getLatLng(@Query(value="address")
                                                                       String address,
                                                                       @Query(value="key")
                                                                       String apiKey)
        Requests full address and geological coordinates from the Google Geocding API. Lat and Lng extracted from JSON response for Google Map Camera update.
        Parameters:
        address - Extracted from a Facility record.
        apiKey - Extracted from application properties file.
        Returns:
        Result

      • getPostal

        @GET(value="/maps/api/geocode/json")
retrofit2.Call<ReverseResult> getPostal(@Query(value="latlng")
                                                                              String latlng)
        Requests full address and geological coordinates from the Google Geocoding API. Postal code extracted from JSON response for database query.
        Parameters:
        latlng - Extracted from LocationManager response.
        Returns:
        ReverseResult
